{"id":1690,"date":"2024-08-26T19:17:54","date_gmt":"2024-08-26T19:17:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1690"},"modified":"2024-11-22T14:07:33","modified_gmt":"2024-11-22T14:07:33","slug":"galladite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/galladite\/","title":{"rendered":"Galladite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Galladite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in the Antisis Port. The stone is hidden on top of some brown shipment crates to the east of the area that is only accessible between 12:00 PM and 1:59 PM<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Gallade<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Antisis City<\/li>\n<li>The time should be between 12:00 and 1:59 PM<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Go to the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center and follow the path east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-antisis-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see a connector you want to enter in the east part of the city.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-east-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the east connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the east connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue east to exit the connector and enter the Antisis Port.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/03-pokemon-unbound-leaving-the-connector-from-the-other-side.jpg\" alt=\"Leaving the connector from the other side. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Leaving the connector from the other side.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go east and then follow the path south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/04-pokemon-unbound-walking-east-and-then-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Walking east and then going south. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking east and then going south.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start following the path east when you can\u2019t go south anymore.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/05-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-east.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path east. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path east.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually see a ladder you can climb to get on top of the yellow shipment containers. <\/p>\n<p>If the path to the ladder is blocked you\u2019ll have to wait for the time to be between 12:00 PM and 1:59 PM.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/06-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-ladder-to-get-on-top-of-the-yellow-containers.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the ladder to get on top of the yellow containers. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the ladder to get on top of the yellow containers.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the north ladder dropping you on top of some brown boxes and interact with the bottom-right crate to get the Galladite.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/galladite\/07-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-galladite-on-top-of-some-brown-boxes.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the Galladite on top of some brown boxes. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the Galladite on top of some brown boxes.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1691,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1690","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1690","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1691"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1690"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1690"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.or